  "keys": ["d"],
  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Subtracting 17 from each side of the given equation yields <math><mn>5</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>17</mn></math>, or <math><mn>5</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>17</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>28</mn></math>.</p><p>Choice A is incorrect; this is the value of <math><mn>5</mn><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>17</mn></math>.</p><p>Choice B is incorrect; this is the value of <math><mi>y</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>17</mn></math>.</p><p>Choice C is incorrect; this is the value of <math><mi>y</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>17</mn></math>.</p>",
